GET /api/services - View services
GET /api/services/:id - View single service
GET /api/appointments/slots - Check available slots
GET /api/settings - View business hours
POST /api/auth/register - Register
POST /api/auth/login - Login

Protected Routes (Auth Required):

POST /api/appointments - Book appointment
GET /api/appointments/my-appointments - View own appointments
GET /api/auth/me - Get current user
PUT /api/auth/profile - Update profile
PUT /api/auth/password - Change password

Admin Only Routes:

All /api/clients routes
POST/PUT/DELETE /api/services
Most /api/appointments management routes
PUT /api/settings